SauceApp
=============================
谢谢使用酱油App，酱油App是一套后台管理系统，可用于ERP、CRM等后台系统开发，提供用户、权限、日志等
管理功能，开发者只要注重业务功能开发即可，方面快速开发符合需求的系统。

Thank you for choosing SauceApp, SauceAPP  is a System Management framework,
provide flexible user and permission administration.

USER FACADE is base on ExtJS and server-side is base on YII Framework.

INSTALLATION
------------

Please make sure the release file is unpacked under a Web-accessible
directory. You shall see the following files and directories:

   	  sauceApp             
      framework/           YII framework source files
      requirements/        requirement checker
	  ext-4.0.7-gpl/       extjs framework
      README               this file
      UPGRADE              upgrading instructions



